---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Week 5: 抗力と摩擦力">
  <h1>Week 5: 抗力と摩擦力</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">なぜ箱を押すのは大変なの？</p>

  <h2>🎯 今日の目標</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>垂直抗力を理解する</li>
    <li>静止摩擦力と動摩擦力の違いを理解する</li>
    <li>斜面での力の分解ができる</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>垂直抗力 N</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <strong>🤔 なぜ床の上に立っても沈まない？</strong><br/>
    床があなたを <strong>押し返している</strong> から！
  </div>

  <h3>垂直抗力とは</h3>
  <p>物体が面に接触しているとき、面から受ける <strong>垂直方向の力</strong></p>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">N = mg</span>
    <p>（水平面上で静止している場合）</p>
  </div>

  <h2>摩擦力</h2>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    表面のデコボコが「かみ合って」動きを妨げる力
  </div>

  <h3>静止摩擦力 vs 動摩擦力</h3>
  <table>
    <tr><th></th><th>静止摩擦力</th><th>動摩擦力</th></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>いつ？</strong></td><td>物体が止まっている</td><td>物体が動いている</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>大きさ</strong></td><td>0 〜 μN（変化する）</td><td>μ'N（一定）</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>特徴</strong></td><td>加えた力と同じ大きさ</td><td>速さによらず一定</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h3>最大静止摩擦力</h3>
  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">f_max = μN</span>
    <p>これを超えると物体が動き出す！</p>
  </div>

  <div class="highlight-box warning">
    <strong>⚠️ 重要：</strong>μ（静止）> μ'（動摩擦）<br/>
    動き出すのが一番大変！一度動けば少し楽になる
  </div>

  <h3>🎮 摩擦力シミュレーター</h3>
  <div class="animation-container">
    <div id="friction-sim">
      <div class="sim-row">
        <div class="sim-display">
          <div class="push-arrow" id="push-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="box" id="sim-box">📦</div>
          <div class="floor"></div>
        </div>
        <canvas id="frictionGraph" width="200" height="150"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="controls">
        <label>
          推力: <span id="force-value">0</span> N
          <input type="range" id="force-slider" min="0" max="100" value="0" />
        </label>
        <label>
          摩擦係数 μ: <span id="mu-value">0.3</span>
          <input type="range" id="mu-slider" min="1" max="8" value="3" />
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-info">
        <p>摩擦力: <span id="static-f">0</span> N</p>
        <p>最大静止摩擦力: <span id="max-f">30</span> N</p>
        <p>状態: <span id="state">静止</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>動摩擦力</h2>
  <div class="formula-box">
    <span class="big-formula">f' = μ'N</span>
    <p>動いている物体にはたらく摩擦力（一定）</p>
  </div>

  <h2>斜面上の摩擦</h2>

  <p>角度 θ の斜面上では：</p>
  <table>
    <tr><th>力</th><th>公式</th></tr>
    <tr><td>垂直抗力</td><td><strong>N = mg cos θ</strong></td></tr>
    <tr><td>滑り落ちる力</td><td>mg sin θ</td></tr>
    <tr><td>最大静止摩擦力</td><td>μ × mg cos θ</td></tr>
  </table>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例：斜面で静止できる条件</h4>
    <p>静止できる ⇔ 滑り落ちる力 ≤ 最大静止摩擦力</p>
    <p>mg sin θ ≤ μ mg cos θ</p>
    <p>tan θ ≤ μ</p>
  </div>

  <h2>例題</h2>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題1：最大静止摩擦力</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>質量 4 kg、μ = 0.5 の物体の最大静止摩擦力は？（g = 10）</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>N = mg = 4 × 10 = 40 N</p>
    <p>f_max = μN = 0.5 × 40 = <strong>20 N</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="example">
    <h4>例題2：斜面</h4>
    <p><strong>問題：</strong>30° の斜面、質量 2 kg、μ = 0.6。静止できる？</p>
    <p><strong>解答：</strong></p>
    <p>滑り落ちる力 = 2 × 10 × sin30° = 20 × 0.5 = 10 N</p>
    <p>N = 2 × 10 × cos30° = 20 × 0.87 = 17.3 N</p>
    <p>最大静止摩擦力 = 0.6 × 17.3 = 10.4 N</p>
    <p>10 < 10.4 なので、<strong>静止できる！</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>📝 今日のポイント</h2>
  <div class="highlight-box">
    <ul>
      <li>✓ 垂直抗力：<strong>N = mg</strong>（水平面）、<strong>N = mg cos θ</strong>（斜面）</li>
      <li>✓ 最大静止摩擦力：<strong>f_max = μN</strong></li>
      <li>✓ 動摩擦力：<strong>f' = μ'N</strong>（一定）</li>
      <li>✓ <strong>μ > μ'</strong>（静止摩擦 > 動摩擦）</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week04/" class="nav-btn secondary">← Week 4</a>
    <a href="/physics-basic/weeks/week06/" class="nav-btn">Week 6 へ →</a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }
  .formula-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .big-formula {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    display: block;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  #friction-sim {
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  .sim-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .sim-display {
    position: relative;
    height: 80px;
    width: 200px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .push-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #ef4444;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .box {
    position: absolute;
    left: 30px;
    bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 2rem;
    transition: left 0.3s;
  }
  .floor {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #a3a3a3, #737373);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  #frictionGraph {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: white;
  }
  .controls {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .controls label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .controls input[type="range"] {
    flex: 1;
  }
  .sim-info {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .sim-info p {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    background: #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  details summary {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>

<script>
  const forceSlider = document.getElementById('force-slider') as HTMLInputElement;
  const muSlider = document.getElementById('mu-slider') as HTMLInputElement;
  const forceValue = document.getElementById('force-value');
  const muValue = document.getElementById('mu-value');
  const staticF = document.getElementById('static-f');
  const maxF = document.getElementById('max-f');
  const state = document.getElementById('state');
  const box = document.getElementById('sim-box');
  const pushArrow = document.getElementById('push-arrow');
  const graphCanvas = document.getElementById('frictionGraph') as HTMLCanvasElement;
  const ctx = graphCanvas?.getContext('2d');

  const mass = 10; // kg
  const g = 10;
  const N = mass * g; // 100 N

  function drawGraph(force: number, mu: number) {
    if (!ctx) return;
    ctx.clearRect(0, 0, 200, 150);
    
    const maxFriction = mu * N;
    const dynamicFriction = mu * 0.8 * N;
    
    // Axes
    ctx.strokeStyle = '#64748b';
    ctx.lineWidth = 1;
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(30, 130);
    ctx.lineTo(190, 130);
    ctx.moveTo(30, 130);
    ctx.lineTo(30, 10);
    ctx.stroke();
    
    // Labels
    ctx.fillStyle = '#64748b';
    ctx.font = '10px sans-serif';
    ctx.fillText('推力', 170, 145);
    ctx.fillText('摩擦力', 5, 15);
    
    // Static region (diagonal line up to max)
    ctx.strokeStyle = '#22c55e';
    ctx.lineWidth = 2;
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(30, 130);
    const maxX = 30 + maxFriction * 1.5;
    const maxY = 130 - maxFriction;
    ctx.lineTo(maxX, maxY);
    ctx.stroke();
    
    // Dynamic region (horizontal line after max)
    ctx.strokeStyle = '#ef4444';
    ctx.setLineDash([5, 3]);
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(maxX, 130 - dynamicFriction);
    ctx.lineTo(190, 130 - dynamicFriction);
    ctx.stroke();
    ctx.setLineDash([]);
    
    // Drop line at transition
    ctx.strokeStyle = '#f59e0b';
    ctx.lineWidth = 1;
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(maxX, maxY);
    ctx.lineTo(maxX, 130 - dynamicFriction);
    ctx.stroke();
    
    // Current point
    let currentY;
    if (force <= maxFriction) {
      currentY = 130 - force;
    } else {
      currentY = 130 - dynamicFriction;
    }
    const currentX = 30 + force * 1.5;
    
    ctx.fillStyle = force <= maxFriction ? '#22c55e' : '#ef4444';
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.arc(Math.min(currentX, 185), currentY, 6, 0, Math.PI * 2);
    ctx.fill();
    
    // Legend
    ctx.font = '9px sans-serif';
    ctx.fillStyle = '#22c55e';
    ctx.fillText('静止', 140, 25);
    ctx.fillStyle = '#ef4444';
    ctx.fillText('動摩擦', 140, 40);
  }

  function update() {
    const force = parseInt(forceSlider?.value || '0');
    const mu = parseInt(muSlider?.value || '3') / 10;
    const maxFriction = mu * N;
    const dynamicFriction = mu * 0.8 * N;

    if (forceValue) forceValue.textContent = force.toString();
    if (muValue) muValue.textContent = mu.toFixed(1);
    if (maxF) maxF.textContent = maxFriction.toFixed(0);
    
    // Push arrow visibility
    if (pushArrow) {
      pushArrow.style.opacity = force > 0 ? '1' : '0';
      pushArrow.textContent = '→'.repeat(Math.min(3, Math.ceil(force / 30)));
    }
    
    drawGraph(force, mu);

    if (force <= maxFriction) {
      // Static
      if (staticF) staticF.textContent = force.toString();
      if (state) {
        state.textContent = force === 0 ? '静止' : '静止（踏ん張り中）';
        state.style.color = '#22c55e';
      }
      if (box) box.style.left = '30px';
    } else {
      // Moving
      const dynamicF = mu * 0.8 * N; // μ' ≈ 0.8μ
      if (staticF) staticF.textContent = dynamicF.toFixed(0) + '（動摩擦）';
      if (state) {
        state.textContent = '滑り出した！';
        state.style.color = '#ef4444';
      }
      if (box) box.style.left = (20 + (force - maxFriction) * 2) + 'px';
    }
  }

  forceSlider?.addEventListener('input', update);
  muSlider?.addEventListener('input', update);
  update();
</script>
